\begin_layout Subsection
Context
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This project covers the work done in conjunction with our master’s thesis
 as part of our master’s programme in informatics, with specialisation in
 game technology, at the Norwegian University of Science and Technology.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The project partially builds upon the findings in the projects presented
 in Section 
