\begin_layout Standard
This section will detail the metrics used to answer our research questions,
 as well as our reasoning behind them.
 We will also look at some potential practical issues and how best to avoid
 them.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Literature Study
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A literature study is one of the most used methods for any research, reviewing
 literature relevant to the subject at hand.
 The purpose of this is to familiarize oneself with the research topic,
 and thus increase the credibility of the research.
 Our sources for this project will be published articles, documentation
 on the web, and other master's theses.
 The topics of our literature study are:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
