\series default
 will cover basic information about the workings and usage of the technology.
 We will also cover the Microsoft Kinect sensor in a bit more detail, as
 this is the one we had available during our project.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
Engines and Frameworks
\series default
 showcases the game engines and frameworks most compatible for use with
 C#.
 We have focused on this since we will be using the Microsoft Kinect, whose
 official SDK is .NET based and thus making C# the preferred language for
 us.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

